membership:
ORCA is a member of EU Platform on Animal Welfare, and expert body of the European Commission. &#xd;
&#xd;
In addition we are members of several international networks: &#xd;
- Eurogroup for Animals, &#xd;
- Species Survival Network, &#xd;
- CEEWeb for Biodiversity &#xd;
- EUROBATS (member of advisory board). &#xd;
&#xd;
ORCA is also a member of important national networks and bodies such as: &#xd;
- National Convention on the European Union (NCEU) &#xd;
- Sectorial Civic Society Organizations (SCSO)&#xd;
Both NCEU and SCSO are platforms for consultations between national authorities and civil sector in relation to EU intergration process&#xd;
- Network Natura 2000, Resource Centre of Serbia, &#xd;
- Council for the Improvement of Food Production Sector, &#xd;
- National Ethical Council for the Welfare of Animals used in Research and local ethical committees at faculties and scientific institutions in Serbia (University of Belgrade - Faculties of Medicine, Biology, Agriculture and Pharmacy; Institute for the Application of Nuclear Energy – INEP, Military Medical Academy, Institute of Virology, Vaccines and Sera “Torlak”).&#xd;
&#xd;
